oot”, Variety <a href=\"http://variety.com/2014/film/news/paul-feig-ghostbusters-comedy-reboot-1201274332/\">has reported</a>. Ivan Reitman, who directed the original movie and Ghostbusters II, dropped out of directing a third movie in the series in March, the report said.</p> <p>It’s not that there were no hilarious women in the original movie, which was written by Dan Aykroyd and Harold Ramis and starred the writers plus Bill Murray. In Ghostbusters, Sigourney Weaver plays a New Yorker whose apartment in <a href=\"http://www.bigwaste.com/photos/ny/ghostbusters/barrett.shtml\">55 Central Park West</a> becomes haunted. So she commutes to <a href=\"http://www.yelp.com/biz/hook-and-ladder-8-ghostbusters-new-york\">Hook &amp; Ladder 8</a> in Tribeca, where the Ghostbusters have set up their headquarters. Before the movie is over she delivers witty ripostes to Murray’s jokes, levitates over a bed and makes love to Rick Moranis. (Weaver has announced her <a href=\"http://www.theguardian.com/film/2014/jun/09/ghostbusters-3-sigourney-weaver-son\">son would appear</a> in the third film.)</p> <p>There should be ample opportunity for the writers of the new movie to riff on the original, which used sex as a metaphor for the ghost apocalypse, with Weaver playing the “gatekeeper”, Moranis playing the “keymaster” and their unearthly offspring embodied by a <a href=\"https://www.google.com/search?q=slavitza+jovan&amp;espv=2&amp;biw=1418&amp;bih=1038&amp;tbm=isch&amp;tbo=u&amp;source=univ&amp;sa=X&amp;ei=IKg1VPztL5Dd7Qb_v4DYDg&amp;ved=0CCAQsAQ\">Serbian supermodel</a>. </p> <p>One thing they’ll have a hard time beating: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m9We2XsVZfc\">that theme song</a>.</p>","productionOffice":"US","hasStoryPackage":"true","trailText":"Bridesmaids’ Paul Feig announces he will direct and co-write reboot about women of paranormal pest extermination team","headline":"Women-led Ghostbusters reboot is official: who they gonna cast?","byline":"Tom McCarthy in Ne